prompts.language_detection:
Detect the language of the following text. Return only a JSON object with the ISO 639-1 language code.

TEXT:
"""{sample}"""

Return JSON:
{{
  "language": "en"
}}

prompts.extract_graph:
Extract a knowledge graph from the text below.

ENTITY TYPES: {entity_types}
RELATION TYPES: {relation_types}

RULES:
- Only extract entities and relations clearly stated in the text
- Each entity: name, type, 1-2 sentence description
- Each relation: source, target, type, brief description, strength (1-10)

TEXT:
"""{text}"""

Return JSON:
{{
  "entities": [{{"name": "...", "type": "...", "description": "..."}}],
  "relations": [{{"source": "...", "target": "...", "type": "...", "description": "...", "strength": 8}}]
}}

prompts.summarize_descriptions:
Summarize multiple descriptions for each item into ONE concise description (1-2 sentences).

ITEMS:
{items_text}

Return JSON:
{{
  "summaries": {{
    "<id>": "<merged description>",
    ...
  }}
}}

